  ('social-worker-moex-07917', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作督導的方式中，下列那一項是屬於團體督導的優點？', '["督導者與被督導者有較高隱密性", "對每位被督導者之督導時間較充足", "對每位被督導者可以充分的面對面討論", "被督導者可學習用不同觀點處理案主或方案的經驗"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6c91d4ef579", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "400", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07918', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '非營利組織大都會擁有可以用貨幣衡量的經濟資源，這些資源也大都有未來之經濟效益，我們稱它們為：', '["資產", "負債", "基金", "餘絀"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6c91d4ef579", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "400", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
